    ss1=!subst $ss1
    texanswer$n=\frac{\left(\begin{array}{c}13\\$getal\end{array}\right)\cdot \left(\begin{array}{c}39\\$[$num - $getal]\end{array}\right)}{\left(\begin{array}{c}52\\$num\end{array}\right)} \approx $answer1 \approx $ans1 

    
    # vraag 2
