    ss2=!subst $ss2
    rr=\left[ \begin{array}{l} P\left(\textrm{$zoveel $card}\right) = \frac{$frequentie}{$number_of_games} = $[$frequentie/$number_of_games] \\ \\  P \left(\textrm{ precies $keer keer $zoveel $card kaarten} \right) = \left(\begin{array}{c}$number\\$keer\end{array}\right) \times $P^{$keer} \times \left( 1 - $P \right)^{$number - $keer} \approx $ans2  \\  \\ \textrm{TexasInstruments Ti83 / GRM : binompdf( $number , $P , $keer ) } \approx $answer2 \approx $ans2 \end{array} \right.
